  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Oral Acarbose Treatment in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Multicenter Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Oral Acarbose Treatment in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
  <sponsors>
