  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Purpose of This Study is to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of Acarbose in Type 2
      Diabetic Patients Using Two Different Formulations of Acarbose 50mg.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study Design:

        -  Multicenter

        -  Phase III

        -  Randomized

        -  Double Blind

        -  Prospective and Comparative

        -  Experiment duration: 105 days

        -  5 visits

        -  Efficacy

        -  Adverse event
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
